e obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Where your data is sent</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n','Privacy Policy','','draft','closed','open','','privacy-policy','','','2024-04-08 00:03:58','2024-04-08 00:03:58','',0,'http://discovery-engineering.local/?page_id=3',0,'page','',0),(4,0,'2024-04-08 00:04:26','2024-04-08 00:04:26','<!-- wp:page-list /-->','Navigation','','publish','closed','closed','','navigation','','','2024-04-08 00:04:26','2024-04-08 00:04:26','',0,'http://discovery-engineering.local/navigation/',0,'wp_navigation','',0),(6,1,'2024-04-08 00:14:16','2024-04-08 00:14:16','','Electrical Engineer Expert Witness - Mark McFarland, P.E.','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2024-04-08 00:14:16','2024-04-08 00:14:16','',2,'http://discovery-engineering.local/?p=6',0,'revision','',0),(8,1,'2024-04-08 00:15:50','2024-04-08 00:15:50','<!-- wp:create-block/two-columns {\"col_code\":\"\\u003ciframe width=\\u0022100%\\u0022 height=\\u0022315\\u0022 src=\\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/\\u002d\\u002dfmbHDUxXc?si=qcefINLbOsmG_Enm\\u0022 title=\\u0022YouTube video player\\u0022 frameborder=\\u00220\\u0022 allow=\\u0022accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\\u0022 referrerpolicy=\\u0022strict-origin-when-cross-origin\\u0022 allowfullscreen\\u003e\\u003c/iframe\\u003e\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-create-block-two-columns\"><section class=\"position-relative \" style=\"padding:100px 0;\" id=\"\"><div class=\"container\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"row justify-content-center\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\" style=\"\" id=\"\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mar