MSEE degree in RF engineering from Drexel University in Philadelphia before moving to Colorado.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003eLastly, I procured the highest credential available in the quality sciences: the Six Sigma Master Black Belt. This required eight graduate courses (24 credit hours) in applied statistics and research at the University of Colorado.\\u003cbr\\u003e\",\"code_block\":\"\"},{\"col_class\":\"col-12\",\"col_style\":\"\",\"col_id\":\"\",\"title\":\"How many years of experience do you have?\",\"content\":\"I have over 25 years of experience as an engineer and ten years of experience in quality sciences and applied research.\",\"code_block\":\"\"},{\"col_class\":\"col-12\",\"col_style\":\"\",\"col_id\":\"\",\"title\":\"Do you have trial experience?\",\"content\":\"Yes – I have testified on behalf of the plaintiff and defense at criminal and civil trials.\",\"code_block\":\"\"}]} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-create-block-content-faqs\"><section class=\"position-relative \" style=\"padding:50px 0;\" id=\"\"><div class=\"container\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"row justify-content-center accordions\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"accordion position-relative col-12\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #D5D8DC;\"><div class=\"position-absolute chevron\"><svg id=\"Layer_2\" data-name=\"Layer 2\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 168.38 321.74\"><defs><style>.cls-1.chevron-right </style></defs><g id=\"Layer_1-2\" data-name=\"Layer 1\"><g><polygon class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" points=\".5 1.17 167.65 160.87 .5 320.57 .5 1.17\"></polygon><path class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" d=\"M1,2.34l165.93,158.53L1,319.4V2.34M0,0v321.74l168.38-160.87L0,0h0Z\"></path></g></g></svg></div><a class=\"button\" style=\"cursor:pointer\">Do you accept cases nationwide?</a><div class=\"accordion-content\"><div class=\"accordion-content-inner\"><p style=\"margin:0px\">Yes, my practice is nationwide.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"accordion position-relative col-12\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #D5D8DC;\"><div class=\"position-absolute chevron\"><svg id=\"Layer_2\" data-name=\"Layer 2\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 168.38 321.74\"><defs><style>.cls-1.chevron-right </style></defs><g id=\"Layer_1-2\" data-name=\"Layer 1\"><g><polygon class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" points=\".5 1.17 167.65 160.87 .5 320.57 .5 1.17\"></polygon><path class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" d=\"M1,2.34l165.93,158.53L1,319.4V2.34M0,0v321.74l168.38-160.87L0,0h0Z\"></path></g></g></svg></div><a class=\"button\" style=\"cursor:pointer\">What kind of cases do you consult on?</a><div class=\"accordion-content\"><div class=\"accordion-content-inner\"><p style=\"margin:0px\">My practice covers various cases involving electrical, electronic, or telecommunications phenomena.<br><br>I work in both civil and criminal cases for the plaintiff or defense.<br><br>I have worked with plaintiff and defense lawyers on civil cases in several fields, including wrongful death, personal injury, product liability, medical malpractice, class action, insurance claims, auto accidents, contract disputes, and more.<br><br>Some criminal cases I’ve worked on have involved securities fraud, homicide, sex trafficking, and home invasion. The criminal cases usually center around cellular, mobile phone, GPS, and other electronic evidence.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"accordion position-relative col-12\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #D5D8DC;\"><div class=\"position-absolute chevron\"><svg id=\"Layer_2\" data-name=\"Layer 2\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 168.38 321.74\"><defs><style>.cls-1.chevron-right </style></defs><g id=\"Layer_1-2\" data-name=\"Layer 1\"><g><polygon class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" points=\".5 1.17 167.65 160.87 .5 320.57 .5 1.17\"></polygon><path class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" d=\"M1,2.34l165.93,158.53L1,319.4V2.34M0,0v321.74l168.38-160.87L0,0h0Z\"></path></g></g></svg></div><a class=\"button\" style=\"cursor:pointer\">What kind of cases do you consult on?</a><div class=\"accordion-content\"><div class=\"accordion-content-inner\"><p style=\"margin:0px\">testing</p></div></div></div><div class=\"accordion position-relative col-12\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #D5D8DC;\"><div class=\"position-absolute chevron\"><svg id=\"Layer_2\" data-name=\"Layer 2\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 168.38 321.74\"><defs><style>.cls-1.chevron-right </style></defs><g id=\"Layer_1-2\" data-name=\"Layer 1\"><g><polygon class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" points=\".5 1.17 167.65 160.87 .5 320.57 .5 1.17\"></polygon><path class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" d=\"M1,2.34l165.93,158.53L1,319.4V2.34M0,0v321.74l168.38-160.87L0,0h0Z\"></path></g></g></svg></div><a class=\"button\" style=\"cursor:pointer\">Do you work for the plaintiff, or do you work for the defense?</a><div class=\"accordion-content\"><div class=\"accordion-content-inner\"><p style=\"margin:0px\">I work for both plaintiff and defense lawyers on civil and criminal cases.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"accordion position-relative col-12\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #D5D8DC;\"><div class=\"position-absolute chevron\"><svg id=\"Layer_2\" data-name=\"Layer 2\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 168.38 321.74\"><defs><style>.cls-1.chevron-right </style></defs><g id=\"Layer_1-2\" data-name=\"Layer 1\"><g><polygon class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" points=\".5 1.17 167.65 160.87 .5 320.57 .5 1.17\"></polygon><path class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" d=\"M1,2.34l165.93,158.53L1,319.4V2.34M0,0v321.74l168.38-160.87L0,0h0Z\"></path></g></g></svg></div><a class=\"button\" style=\"cursor:pointer\">Are you licensed to practice engineering?</a><div class=\"accordion-content\