\"\"><div class=\"row justify-content-between flex-row-reverse\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\" style=\"\" id=\"\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Practice Areas</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"arrows\"} -->\n<ul class=\"arrows\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Electrical &amp; Electronics Engineering</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Telecommunications Engineering</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Wireless Engineering</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>GPS &amp; Cellular Evidence Analysis</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Quality Sciences &amp; Applied Research</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mark McFarland, P.E., is a licensed Professional Electrical Engineer, a Board Certified Forensic Engineer, and a statistician. He holds a Bachelor of Science in Electrical Engineering (BSEE) from Lehigh University in Bethlehem, PA.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In addition, he holds a Master’s degree in Telecommunications Engineering and a second Master’s degree in Engineering Management, both from the University of Colorado at Boulder.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With over 25 years of experience as an engineer and ten years of experience in quality sciences and applied research, he can provide unbiased, clear, and timely explanations nationwide.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[button href=\"/contact/\"]Start to Solve Your Case[/button]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode --></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\" style=\"\" id=\"\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"><img src=\"http://discovery-engineering.local/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Mark-McFarland.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\" id=\"\"/></div></div></div></section></div>\n<!-- /wp:create-block/content-image -->\n\n<!-- wp:create-block/content-block {\"section_style\":\"padding-bottom:0px;\",\"section_class\":\"bg-light\",\"col_class\":\"col-lg-12 text-center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-create-block-content-block\"><section class=\"position-relative bg-light\" style=\"padding:50px 0;padding-bottom:0px;\" id=\"\"><div class=\"container\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"row justify-content-center\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"col-lg-12 text-center\" style=\"\" id=\"\" data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Forensic Engineering &amp; Applied Research Expertise</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div></div></section></div>\n<!-- /wp:create-block/content-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:create-block/boxes-title-content {\"section_style\":\"padding-top:5px;\",\"section_class\":\"bg-light\",\"columns\":[{\"col_class\":\"col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch\",\"col_style\":\"margin: 20px 0;paddin\",\"col_id\":\"02\",\"img\":\"\",\"title\":\"Wireless and Telecommunications Engineering\",\"content\":\"Over 25 years of experience in research, design, analysis, \\u0026 measurement of cellular, GPS, 3G–5G, LTE, public safety comm systems, satellite, Internet, wireless, RF, Wi-Fi, radar, networks, data communications, communications protocols and standards, instrumentation, and control systems.\",\"inner_col_style\":\"box-shadow:0px 0px 3px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);padding:20px;\",\"inner_col_class\":\"bg-white\"},{\"col_class\":\"col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch\",\"col_style\":\"margin: 20px 0;s\",\"col_id\":\"03\",\"inner_col_style\":\"box-shadow:0px 0px 3px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);padding:20px;\",\"inner_col_class\":\"bg-white\",\"img\":\"\",\"title\":\"GPS and Cellular Evidence Analysis\",\"content\":\"Understanding GPS, cell phone, \\u0026 base station evidence is critical. I present data and uncertainties in easy to understand maps, animations, timelines, and tables. These can show patterns of communications, whereabouts, and activity. I map \\u0026 analyze records from all manufacturers and carriers.\"},{\"col_class\":\"col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch\",\"col_style\":\"margin: 20px 0;\",\"col_id\":\"01\",\"img\":\"\",\"title\":\"Electrical and Electronics Engineering\",\"content\":\"I investigate electrical and electronic components, equipment, systems, \\u0026 devices to support litigation related to design, use, defects, malfunctions, modifications, and equipment breakdown for civil and criminal matters.\\n\",\"inner_col_style\":\"box-shadow:0px 0px 3px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);padding:20px;\",\"inner_col_class\":\"bg-white\"},{\"col_class\":\"col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch\",\"col_style\":\"margin: 20px 0;\",\"col_id\":\"04\",\"inner_col_style\":\"box-shadow:0px 0px 3px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);padding:20px;\",\"inner_col_class\":\"bg-white\",\"img\":\"\",\"title\":\"Quality Sciences and Applied Research\",\"content\":\"Understanding variability is crucial to improving and controlling any process. I bring scholarship \\u0026amp; practical experience in applied research \\u0026amp; quality sciences to help clients understand variability and improve outcomes.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003eStudies show that most published scientific research cannot be reproduced [NAS, 2018]. The scientific, financial, and legal consequences of irreproducible research, from arbitrary research methods to improper analyses, are enormous. I ensure that solid and defensible methods inform your decisions.\"}]} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-create-block-boxes-title-content\"><section class=\"position-relative bg-light\" style=\"padding:50px 0;padding-top:5px;\" id=\"\"><div class=\"container\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"row justify-content-center\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch\" style=\"margin: 20px 0;paddin\"><div class=\"bg-white\" style=\"box-shadow:0px 0px 3px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);padding:20px;\"><h3>Wireless and Telecommunications Engineering</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom:0px\">Over 25 years of experience in research, design, analysis, & measurement of cellular, GPS, 3G–5G, LTE, public safety comm systems, satellite, Internet, wireless, RF, Wi-Fi, radar, networks, data communications, communications protocols and standards, instrumentation, and control systems.</p></div></div><div class=\"col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch\" style=\"margin: 20px 0;s\"><div class=\"bg-white\" style=\"box-shadow:0px 0px 3px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);padding:20px;\"><h3>GPS and Cellular Evidence Analysis</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom:0px\">Understanding GPS, cell phone, & base station evidence is critical. I present data and uncertainties in easy to understand maps, animations, timelines, and tables. These can show patterns of communications, whereabouts, and activity. I map & analyze records from all manufacturers and carriers.</p></div></div><div class=\"col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch\" style=\"margin: 20px 0;\"><div class=\"bg-white\" style=\"box-shadow:0px 0px 3px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);padding:20px;\"><h3>Electrical and Electronics Engineering</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom:0px\">I investigate electrical and electronic components, equipment, systems, & devices to support litigation related to design, use, defects, malfunctions, modifications, and equipment breakdown for civil and criminal matters.\n</p></div></div><div class=\"col-md-6 d-flex align-items-stretch\" style=\"margin: 20px 0;\"><div class=\"bg-white\" style=\"box-shadow:0px 0px 3px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);padding:20px;\"><h3>Quality Sciences and Applied Research</h3><p style=\"margin-bottom:0px\">Understanding variability is crucial to improving and controlling any process. I bring scholarship &amp; practical experience in applied research &amp; quality sciences to help clients understand variability and improve outcomes.<br><br>Studies show that most published scientific research cannot be reproduced [NAS, 2018]. The scientific, financial, and legal consequences of irreproducible research, from arbitrary research methods to improper analyses, are enormous. I ensure that solid and defensible methods inform your decisions.</p></div></div></div></div></section></div>\n<!-- /wp:create-block/boxes-title-content -->\n\n<!-- wp:create-block/content-block {\"section_style\":\"border-top:1px solid black;padding-bottom:0px;\",\"col_class\":\"col-lg-12 text-center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-create-block-content-block\"><section class=\"position-relative \" style=\"padding:50px 0;border-top:1px solid black;padding-bottom:0px;\" id=\"\"><div class=\"container\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"row justify-content-center\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"col-lg-12 text-center\" style=\"\" id=\"\" data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ensure Defensible Methods Are Informing Your Decisions</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div></div></section></div>\n<!-- /wp:create-block/content-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:create-block/content-image {\"section_style\":\"border-bottom:1px solid black;padding-top:50px;\",\"col_class\":\"col-lg-7\",\"col_image\":\"http://discovery-engineering.local/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Defensible-Methods.jpg\",\"col_image_class\":\"col-lg-5\",\"image_style\":\"filter:grayscale(1);\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-create-block-content-image\"><section class=\"position-relative \" style=\"padding:50px 0;border-bottom:1px solid black;padding-top:50px;\" id=\"\"><div class=\"container\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"row justify-content-center\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\" style=\"\" id=\"\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Judicial decisions may be based on testimony from an expert whose opinion may (unknowingly) be based upon irreproduciable research. The research methods courts accept to gain knowledge must be reliable and follow established and defensible procedures.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The financial and legal consequences of improper scientific research methods are enormous.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mr. McFarland’s expertise in engineering and applied research is recognized by legal, insurance, industry, and government clients alike which make him an ideal electrical engineer expert witness.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[button href=\"/contact/\"]Win Your Case Now[/button]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode --></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\" style=\"\" id=\"\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"><img src=\"http://discovery-engineering.local/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Defensible-Methods.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;filter:grayscale(1);\" id=\"\"/></div></div></div></section></div>\n<!-- /wp:create-block/content-image -->\n\n<!-- wp:create-block/content-block {\"section_class\":\"bg-light\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-create-block-content-block\"><section class=\"position-relative bg-light\" style=\"padding:50px 0;\" id=\"\"><div class=\"container\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"row justify-content-center\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"col-lg-9 text-center\" style=\"\" id=\"\" data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">In The Media</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div></div></section></div>\n<!-- /wp:create-block/content-block -->\n\n<!-- wp:create-block/boxes-title-content {\"section_style\":\"padding-top:0px;\",\"section_class\":\"bg-light\",\"columns\":[{\"col_class\":\"col-md-6\",\"col_style\":\"\",\"col_id\":\"\",\"inner_col_style\":\"\",\"inner_col_class\":\"\",\"img\":\"http://discovery-engineering.local/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/true-law-stories-forensics-google-data-and-key-fobs-in-trial.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"content\":\"\",\"code_block\":\"\\u003caudio controls style=\\u0022width:100%;\\u0022\\u003e\\n  \\u003csource src=\\u0022/wp-content/themes/latinowebstudio/audios/true-law-stories-forensics-google-data-and-key-fobs-in-trial.mp3\\u0022 type=\\u0022audio/mpeg\\u0022\\u003e\\n\\u003c/audio\\u003e\",\"img_class\"