},{\"col_class\":\"col-12\",\"col_style\":\"\",\"col_id\":\"\",\"title\":\"Do you work for the plaintiff, or do you work for the defense?\",\"content\":\"I work for both plaintiff and defense lawyers on civil and criminal cases.\",\"code_block\":\"\"},{\"col_class\":\"col-12\",\"col_style\":\"\",\"col_id\":\"\",\"title\":\"Are you licensed to practice engineering?\",\"content\":\"Yes, I am a licensed and Board certified engineer. My Board certification comes from the National Academy of Forensic Engineers. Additionally, I am an NCEES “Record Holder, ” meaning I can typically get licensed in any state within 30 days.\",\"code_block\":\"\"},{\"col_class\":\"col-12\",\"col_style\":\"\",\"col_id\":\"\",\"title\":\"What is your availability?\",\"content\":\"I am accepting new cases and am flexible and available on my clients’ schedules. I take pride in meeting all my clients’ deadlines.\",\"code_block\":\"\"},{\"col_class\":\"col-12\",\"col_style\":\"\",\"col_id\":\"\",\"title\":\"What is your billing rate?\",\"content\":\"My rates are very reasonable. I have two set rates for testimony time, such as in deposition or trial. The second, a lower rate, is for all other time (research, report writing, etc.) I collect an initial retainer and invoice against that.\",\"code_block\":\"\"},{\"col_class\":\"col-12\",\"col_style\":\"\",\"col_id\":\"\",\"title\":\"What is your educational background?\",\"content\":\"I’ve been blessed with the opportunity to gain excellent academic credentials.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003eI have a Bachelor of Science in Electrical Engineering (BSEE) from Lehigh University in Bethlehem, PA. My first Master’s degree is in Telecommunications Engineering, and my second Master’s degree is in Engineering Management- both from the University of Colorado at Boulder. I also completed about 2/3 of an MSEE degree in RF engineering from Drexel University in Philadelphia before moving to Colorado.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003eLastly, I procured the highest credential available in the quality sciences: the Six Sigma Master Black Belt. This required eight graduate courses (24 credit hours) in applied statistics and research at the University of Colorado.\\u003cbr\\u003e\",\"code_block\":\"\"},{\"col_class\":\"col-12\",\"col_style\":\"\",\"col_id\":\"\",\"title\":\"How many years of experience do you have?\",\"content\":\"I have over 25 years of experience as an engineer and ten years of experience in quality sciences and applied research.\",\"code_block\":\"\"},{\"col_class\":\"col-12\",\"col_style\":\"\",\"col_id\":\"\",\"title\":\"Do you have trial experience?\",\"content\":\"Yes – I have testified on behalf of the plaintiff and defense at criminal and civil trials.\",\"code_block\":\"\"}]} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-create-block-content-faqs\"><section class=\"position-relative \" style=\"padding:50px 0;\" id=\"\"><div class=\"container\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"row justify-content-center accordions\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"accordion position-relative col-12\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #D5D8DC;\"><div class=\"position-absolute chevron\"><svg id=\"Layer_2\" data-name=\"Layer 2\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 168.38 321.74\"><defs><style>.cls-1.chevron-right </style></defs><g id=\"Layer_1-2\" data-name=\"Layer 1\"><g><polygon class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" points=\".5 1.17 167.65 160.87 .5 320.57 .5 1.17\"></polygon><path class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" d=\"M1,2.34l165.93,158.53L1,319.4V2.34M0,0v321.74l168.38-160.87L0,0h0Z\"></path></g></g></svg></div><a class=\"button\" style=\"cursor:pointer\">Do you accept cases nationwide?</a><div class=\"accordion-content\"><div class=\"accordion-content-inner\"><p style=\"margin:0px\">Yes, my practice is nationwide.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"accordion position-relative col-12\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #D5D8DC;\"><div class=\"position-absolute chevron\"><svg id=\"Layer_2\"