><svg id=\"Layer_2\" data-name=\"Layer 2\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 168.38 321.74\"><defs><style>.cls-1.chevron-right </style></defs><g id=\"Layer_1-2\" data-name=\"Layer 1\"><g><polygon class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" points=\".5 1.17 167.65 160.87 .5 320.57 .5 1.17\"></polygon><path class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" d=\"M1,2.34l165.93,158.53L1,319.4V2.34M0,0v321.74l168.38-160.87L0,0h0Z\"></path></g></g></svg></div><a class=\"button\" style=\"cursor:pointer\">What kind of cases do you consult on?</a><div class=\"accordion-content\"><div class=\"accordion-content-inner\"><p style=\"margin:0px\">testing</p></div></div></div><div class=\"accordion position-relative col-12\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #D5D8DC;\"><div class=\"position-absolute chevron\"><svg id=\"Layer_2\" data-name=\"Layer 2\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 168.38 321.74\"><defs><style>.cls-1.chevron-right </style></defs><g id=\"Layer_1-2\" data-name=\"Layer 1\"><g><polygon class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" points=\".5 1.17 167.65 160.87 .5 320.57 .5 1.17\"></polygon><path class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" d=\"M1,2.34l165.93,158.53L1,319.4V2.34M0,0v321.74l168.38-160.87L0,0h0Z\"></path></g></g></svg></div><a class=\"button\" style=\"cursor:pointer\">Do you work for the plaintiff, or do you work for the defense?</a><div class=\"accordion-content\"><div class=\"accordion-content-inner\"><p style=\"margin:0px\">I work for both plaintiff and defense lawyers on civil and criminal cases.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"accordion position-relative col-12\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #D5D8DC;\"><div class=\"position-absolute chevron\"><svg id=\"Layer_2\" data-name=\"Layer 2\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 168.38 321.74\"><defs><style>.cls-1.chevron-right </style></defs><g id=\"Layer_1-2\" data-name=\"Layer 1\"><g><polygon class=\"cls-1 chevr