 to gain excellent academic credentials.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003eI have a Bachelor of Science in Electrical Engineering (BSEE) from Lehigh University in Bethlehem, PA. My first Master’s degree is in Telecommunications Engineering, and my second Master’s degree is in Engineering Management- both from the University of Colorado at Boulder. I also completed about 2/3 of an MSEE degree in RF engineering from Drexel University in Philadelphia before moving to Colorado.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003eLastly, I procured the highest credential available in the quality sciences: the Six Sigma Master Black Belt. This required eight graduate courses (24 credit hours) in applied statistics and research at the University of Colorado.\\u003cbr\\u003e\",\"code_block\":\"\"},{\"col_class\":\"col-12\",\"col_style\":\"\",\"col_id\":\"\",\"title\":\"How many years of experience do you have?\",\"content\":\"I have over 25 years of experience as an engineer and ten years of experience in quality sciences and applied research.\",\"code_block\":\"\"},{\"col_class\":\"col-12\",\"col_style\":\"\",\"col_id\":\"\",\"title\":\"Do you have trial experience?\",\"content\":\"Yes – I have testified on behalf of the plaintiff and defense at criminal and civil trials.\",\"code_block\":\"\"}]} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-create-block-content-faqs\"><section class=\"position-relative \" style=\"padding:50px 0;\" id=\"\"><div class=\"container\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"row justify-content-center accordions\" style=\"\" id=\"\"><div class=\"accordion position-relative col-12\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #D5D8DC;\"><div class=\"position-absolute chevron\"><svg id=\"Layer_2\" data-name=\"Layer 2\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 168.38 321.74\"><defs><style>.cls-1.chevron-right </style></defs><g id=\"Layer_1-2\" data-name=\"Layer 1\"><g><polygon class=\"cls-1 chevron-right\" style=\"stroke-width:0px\" points=\".5 1.17 167.65 160.87 .5 320.57 .5 1.17\"></polygon><path 